oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Various demo performances - Cedarwood Publishing Company - 1963-12-13
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Various demo performances, featuring songs written by Roy Botkin (songwriter), Swan, Ackerman, Ashworth, and Bentley, according to tape case. Recorded on December 13, 1963 at Cedarwood Studios (Nashville, Tenn.)
